00:38:15,200 --> 00:38:16,600
She is worth it.

351
00:38:18,900 --> 00:38:20,200
Can you tell her that?

352
00:38:21,000 --> 00:38:22,000
Yeah.

353
00:38:22,800 --> 00:38:23,800
I will.

354
00:38:29,500 --> 00:38:32,400
Guys, i don't want to ruin
a beautiful moment, but look.

355
00:38:46,600 --> 00:38:48,300
We talked about this.

356
00:38:50,100 --> 00:38:52,300
The night we watched
the sunset up here.

357
00:39:00,100 --> 00:39:01,400
You said that...

358
00:39:02,900 --> 00:39:06,200
You wanted to ride the wind
all the way home.

359
00:39:08,900 --> 00:39:10,200
You remembered.

360
00:39:16,100 --> 00:39:17,500
Tell her i'm ready.

361
00:39:18,600 --> 00:39:19,600
He's ready.

362
00:39:20,900 --> 00:39:22,000
To go now.

